(define Main-helpText (PreludeC-45Types-u--foldMap_Foldable_List csegen-18 (lambda (eta-0) eta-0) (cons "idris2-evm-cov - EVM Semantic Coverage Analysis\xa;\xa;USAGE:\xa;  idris2-evm-cov [options] <project-dir>\xa;  idris2-evm-cov --ipkg <package.ipkg> [options]\xa;\xa;DESCRIPTION:\xa;  Analyzes EVM code coverage using Idris2's --dumpcases for static branch\xa;  analysis (denominator) and Chez Scheme profiler for runtime hits (numerator).\xa;\xa;OPTIONS:\xa;  -h, --help          Show this help message\xa;  -v, --version       Show version\xa;  --verbose           Verbose output\xa;  --json              Output in JSON format\xa;  --text              Output in text format (default)\xa;  --markdown          Output in Markdown format\xa;  --oneline           One-line summary output\xa;  --dumpcases         Static analysis only (no profiler)\xa;  --threshold <N>     Coverage threshold percentage (default: 80)\xa;  -o, --output <dir>  Output directory for reports\xa;  --ipkg <path>       Path to .ipkg file\xa;\xa;EXAMPLES:\xa;  # Analyze a project\xa;  idris2-evm-cov ~/code/idris2-evm\xa;\xa;  # JSON output for CI\xa;  idris2-evm-cov --json ~/code/idris2-evm\xa;\xa;  # Static analysis only\xa;  idris2-evm-cov --dumpcases ~/code/idris2-evm\xa;\xa;COVERAGE MODEL:\xa;  Denominator: Canonical branches from --dumpcases (excludes void/uninhabited)\xa;  Numerator:   Branches hit during test execution (Chez profiler)\xa;\xa;  Branch Classifications:\xa;    - Canonical:        Reachable branches (included in coverage %)\xa;    - ExcludedNoClauses: Void/uninhabited patterns (excluded)\xa;    - BugUnhandledInput: Partial code bugs (flagged)\xa;    - OptimizerNat:     Nat\x2192;Integer artifacts (non-semantic)\xa;    - Unknown:          Investigate manually" '())))
